column2: #TEXT FOR IF I INCLUDE MY MODEL:   My first step was to create a multi-level model. The model below uses Family Decision Making as the outcome. The inputs were gender, country, and an interaction between age and country.
#model I used for FDM. Looking to incorporate this somehow? Not sure how.
model.FDM_outcome <- lmer(FDM ~  SES + ChGender + AgeCM + Country + AgeCM*Country + (1|ID), data = data)
